Jane Fonda, 81, who recently celebrated the news that her cancer was in remission, wowed as she donned a snakeskin print sequinned blazer teamed with trousers. The Barbarella star matched her attire with a pair of black leather boots. The actress wore her grey tresses in her signature style and accessorised her look with gold earrings. The Academy Award winner sported light makeup adding a smokey eye with a nude lip. Jane posed for pictures alongside Mrs Doubtfire actress, Sally, 76, looked chic in a tan coat paired with black pants and white trainers. Lily, 83, wore a graphic T-shirt underneath a blue pantsuit, which she teamed with a red cherry necklace.